import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"what-is-this"}}>{`What is this?`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`We are a community of software developers working to make better real estate software.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"whats-better"}}>{`What's Better?`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Decentralized data (Customer Control.)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Software is integrated by default.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`No vendor lock-in.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`No customer lock-out!`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Open source, plug-and-play APIs to build-on.  Fast.`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"who"}}>{`Who`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Yodata`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Real Estate Digital`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`RoqLogic`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Moxiworks`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`HSF`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Real-Living`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`SmarterAgent`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Imprev`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Contactually`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
